To run this implementation run the script file by typing the following command on the terminal.

./cuda01 5 10 1000 1

where 
the first argument 5 indicate the dimension of LP to be solved;
the second argument 10 indicate the number of runs for average readings;
the third argument 1000 indicate the batch-size of LP to be solved;
the last argument 1 indicate the number of streams to be created (0 for no streaming, 1 to create only one stream or 'n' for creating n streams).

